            <div class="article-intro">
                <p data-i18n="intro">
                    The past year belonged to reasoning and agentic AI. However, the current topic is Physical AI – the emergence of artificial intelligence
                    into the physical world through robotics, autonomous logistics, and smart operations. Lucie Melicharová participated in the Exponential
                    Circles meeting, where she joined leading experts to discuss what this revolution means for business and human resources.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="article-image">
                <img src="/images/article2.jpg" alt="Preparing Leaders for the Era of Physical AI" />
            </div>

            <section class="article-section">
                <h2 data-i18n="section1Title">Why is Physical AI changing the game in HR and Executive Search?</h2>
                <p data-i18n="section1Para1">
                    For learn2grow, Physical AI is not just a technological trend, but a fundamental change in how we define leadership and work teams.
                    Searching for top managers is no longer just about people. Future leaders must be able to manage hybrid ecosystems where humans, AI, and
                    humanoid robots function side-by-side.
                </p>
            </section>

