                    Details about the content of this meeting of investors, developers, and leaders can be found on the official event page:
                </p>
                <a
                    href="https://www.redbuttonedu.cz/udalosti/exponential-circles-1-investori-vyvojari-leaderi-i-uzivatele-u-jednoho-stolu"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="external-link-btn"
